---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Servicios - Omar Fuentes" description="Conoce mis servicios: diseño web, SEO, optimización y soporte para que tu sitio genere resultados.">
  
  <main class="pt-24 pb-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
      
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black mb-6">Mis Servicios</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Soluciones web profesionales diseñadas para hacer crecer tu negocio. Desde el diseño hasta el SEO, 
          te ayudo a crear una presencia online que convierte visitantes en clientes.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Services Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
        
        <!-- Diseño Web -->
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-blue to-accent-blue rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-black">Diseño Web Personalizado</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Diseños únicos y modernos adaptados a tu marca. Sitios web responsive que se ven perfectos en cualquier dispositivo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- SEO -->
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-green to-accent-green rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-black">Optimización SEO</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Mejora tu visibilidad en Google. Estrategias SEO efectivas para aumentar tráfico orgánico y posicionamiento.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Desarrollo -->
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-yellow to-accent-yellow rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-black">Desarrollo Rápido</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Sitios web ultrarrápidos optimizados para rendimiento. Tecnología moderna para la mejor experiencia de usuario.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- E-commerce -->
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-blue to-accent-blue rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-black">Tiendas Online</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            E-commerce profesional para vender tus productos. Integración con pasarelas de pago y gestión de inventario.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- WordPress -->
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-green to-accent-green rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-black">WordPress</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Desarrollo y personalización de WordPress. Temas a medida, plugins y optimización para CMS.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Soporte -->
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-yellow to-accent-yellow rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-black">Soporte y Mantenimiento</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Mantenimiento continuo, actualizaciones de seguridad y soporte técnico para mantener tu sitio funcionando.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Process Section -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-black text-center">Mi Proceso de Trabajo</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-blue to-accent-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-black">Reunión Inicial</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Reunión breve para entender tu objetivo y tu cliente ideal</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-green to-accent-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-black">Diseño y Estructura</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Diseño y estructura enfocada en conversión (sin relleno)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-yellow to-accent-yellow rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-black">Desarrollo</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Desarrollo rápido y optimizado para SEO y velocidad</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-blue to-accent-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-black">Revisión y Ajustes</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Revisión contigo + ajustes finales antes de publicar</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-green to-accent-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">5</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-black">Entrega</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Entrega + soporte post-lanzamiento (garantía incluida)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <section class="rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-blue via-primary-yellow to-primary-green p-12 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">¿Listo para comenzar tu proyecto?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8 opacity-90">
          Contáctame hoy y comencemos a construir tu sitio web profesional
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="https://wa.me/573107851074" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white text-primary-blue px-8 py-4 font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all transform hover:scale-105">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
            </svg>
            WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:contacto@omarfuentes.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition-all transform hover:scale-105">
            Email
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
